title: At least 27 people dead and 100 missing after boat capsizes in Nigeria
description: About 200 passengers, mostly women, were on vessel that sunk in Niger RiverAt least 27 people have died and more than 100 are missing after a boat capsized in northern Nigeria, authorities have said.About 200 passengers were on the boat that was going from the state of Kogi to neighbouring state of Niger when it capsized on the Niger River, the Niger state emergency management agency spokesperson, Ibrahim Audu, told the Associated Press. title: Honeymoon horror: Newlywed bride mysteriously found dead in Miami
description: A Polish bride's honeymoon in Miami turned tragic when she died 23 days after her wedding. Aleksandra Leczycka and her husband were found unconscious, suspected initially of being drugged and robbed. A re-investigation revealed she likely consumed psychoactive substances voluntarily, leading to her death. Aleksandra's husband has not commented on the incident.
author: TOI World Desk

title: ‘Coordinated psy-op’: Elon Musk echoes Joe Rogan’s defence of Trump
description: Elon Musk defended President-elect Donald Trump, branding criticism against him as a "coordinated psychological operation". Musk echoed podcast host Joe Rogan's claims that backlash towards Trump is orchestrated to distort public perception. Rogan suggested that differing treatment of political figures reveals hypocrisy. Both Musk and Rogan have publicly supported Trump, amplifying these perspectives to their massive audiences.
author: TOI World Desk
